videos.description: SMU RB Xavier Jones coughs up the ball behind the line of scrimmage and Jaylon Ferguson recovers for Louisiana Tech.
videos.headline: LA Tech forces SMU turnover on first play from scrimmage

videos.description: SMU QB Ben Hicks has his pass picked off by Secdrick Cooper who breaks several tackles on his 31-yard return, getting all the way to the SMU 30-yard line.
videos.headline: LA Tech returns INT into SMU territory

videos.description: On fourth-and-goal from the 1-yard line, Louisiana Tech QB J'Mar Smith pounds it up the gut to give the Bulldogs an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Bulldogs strike first as Smith sneaks it in

videos.description: Louisiana Tech's defense forces its third turnover in as many possessions as Amik Robertson picks off Ben Hicks' pass and returns it back 45 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: LA Tech scores on pick-six

videos.description: Louisiana Tech WR Teddy Veal catches a short pass and makes a defender miss en route to a 6-yard touchdown, putting LA Tech ahead 21-3.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Veal jukes his way into end zone

videos.description: The Louisiana Tech defense continues to shine in the Frisco Bowl, picking off SMU QB Ben Hicks for a third time and taking it back all the way for another touchdown.
videos.headline: Bulldogs earn second pick-six of first half

videos.description: Bulldogs QB J'Mar Smith lofts a pass to the end zone and Teddy Veal hauls it in for a 27-yard score, giving Louisiana Tech a commanding 35-3 lead.
videos.headline: LA Tech airs it out for TD

videos.description: The Bulldogs come up with another turnover, this time forcing SMU RB Braeden West to fumble.
videos.headline: LA Tech forces fifth turnover of first half

videos.description: Louisiana Tech QB J'Mar Smith throws a quick pass to Kam McKnight who jumps up and makes an impressive catch over his defender for an 11-yard score.
videos.headline: McKnight makes leaping grab for Bulldogs TD

videos.description: SMU WR Trey Quinn battles his defender in the end zone and wins the jump ball for a 9-yard touchdown just before halftime.
videos.headline: Mustangs score on Quinn's contested catch in end zone

videos.description: Bulldogs WR Teddy Veal shows off his quickness, juking past two SMU defenders on his way to a 34-yard gain.
videos.headline: LA Tech's Veal shakes two defenders

videos.description: Louisiana Tech's defense continues its dominant showing as Bulldogs DE Eric Kendzior falls on SMU QB Ben Hicks' fumble deep in SMU territory.
videos.headline: LA Tech defense picks up sixth forced turnover

videos.description: Leading 51-10 late in the fourth quarter, Louisiana Tech head coach Skip Holtz is showered in Gatorade by QB J'Mar Smith.
videos.headline: Coach Holtz gets Gatorade bath in fourth quarter

videos.description: Louisiana Tech coach Skip Holtz says his team showed a lot of toughness and resilience throughout the season which was on display in their decisive bowl victory against SMU.
videos.headline: Coach Holtz 'really proud' of team after Frisco Bowl win

videos.description: Mike Couzens and John Congemi break down LA Tech's 51-10 victory over SMU in the DXL Frisco Bowl, citing the Bulldogs' dominant defense as the deciding factor in the game.
videos.headline: Louisiana Tech routs SMU to win Frisco Bowl

videos.description: The Bulldogs return two of Ben Hicks' three interceptions for touchdowns, and QB J'Mar Smith passes for 216 yards and three TDs to lead Louisiana Tech to a dominating 51-10 win.
videos.headline: LA Tech cruises to DXL Frisco Bowl victory over SMU
